    "caption_text": "ZARA presents \"Le Dîner\"\n \nA quiet evening in one of Madrid’s most elegant restaurants takes an unexpected turn when a small group of strangers decides to stay for dinner. As spontaneous conversations spark and a mysterious visitor arrives, the night unfolds into an encounter none of them will soon forget.\n \nStarring Rossy de Palma @rossydpalma, Damson Idris @damsonidris, Dylan Penn @iamdylanpenn, Chucho Valdés @chuchovaldesmusic with Diane Kruger @dianekruger & Vincent Cassel @vincentcassel.\n\nA short film directed by Santos Bacana @santosbacana & Rogelio Gonzalez @roger_gonzalez_\nProduced by Little Spain @little.spain\n\nCinematographer  Arnau Valls Colomer @arnauvallscolomer\nStylist Harry Lambert @harry_lambert\nArt Director Jose Tirado @josetiradoad\n\nTo watch this short movie with subtitles please visit zara.com or the Zara app\n\n#zara",
